HEADWORD: Illapsable
<hw>Il*laps"a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>il-</ets> not + <ets>lapsable</ets>.]</ety> <def>Incapable of
slipping, or of error.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Morally immutable and <qex>illapsable</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Glanvill.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

